# 🌍 AI Travel Planner

**Smart Itinerary Generation Powered by DeepSeek**  
*Your Personal Travel Assistant for Perfect Trip Planning*

🚀 [Live Demo](#) | 📱 [Download APK](#) | 📜 [API Documentation](#)

---

## ✨ Features

- **AI-Powered Itineraries**: Generate detailed daily plans based on destination, dates, and travel preferences
- **Multi-Modal Authentication**: Secure JWT login + guest mode
- **Offline-First**: Hive local storage for itinerary access without internet
- **Cross-Platform**: Android/iOS/Web ready with Flutter
- **Smart Suggestions**: AI-curated activity recommendations
- **Travel History**: Save and revisit past itineraries

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

**Frontend**  
(https://flutter.dev)  
**Backend**  
(https://nodejs.org)  
(https://www.mongodb.com)

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

```bash
# Clone & Run
git clone https://github.com/imhafzan/ai-travel-planner.git
cd ai-travel-planner
flutter pub get
flutter run
```

